herwise, I can wrap `logs` in `useMemo`, or just reference `logs.length`.\n\n\n**Evaluating cryptographic visual**\n\nI am now pleased with the cryptographic signing flow visual, and appreciate the senior frontend engineering practices used. I am going to evaluate what other improvements can be made, and will check the rendering of the cryptographic signing flow. I will review the design of the container and headers, next.\n\n\n"}}
